strings: <voice_0x01001493><se_low>High Priest Rolo: You...help me! His Holiness is in danger! An evil creature has forced its way into his chamber!
<voice_0x01001494><se_low>High Priest Rolo: You have to help him!
<voice_0x01001495><se_low>High Priest Rolo: And...don't forget to mention...
<voice_0x01001496><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Tell His Holiness that it was High Priest Rolo who sent for help first!
